title: Introducing Michael Kors Sneakers
description:
By land, by sea or sky—hit the road in style in our new collection of super-glam sneakers, decked out with luxe textures, metallic accents and high-shine studs. 

Discover the complete collection at www.michaelkors.com 

#JetSetGo
